{"tid":1583894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六月至今拘近 1,500 人　僅檢控 207 人　警方否認濫捕     警放3100枚催淚彈 590發橡膠彈","createTime":"2019-09-21T00:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T12:44:11.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"82f50eb3fc39c2983c98d5136a381bb51f7d77e7","tid":1583894,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:40:42.000Z","msg":"六月至今拘近 1,500 人　僅檢控 207 人　警方否認濫捕<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動持續，警方指至今拘捕了 1,474 人，落案檢控當中 207 人，包括 79 人參與暴動，40 人被控非法集結等；在今天記者會上被問到警方拘捕逾 1,400 人，當中只有 207 人被檢控，是否反映警方濫捕，警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥指，被捕人士保釋候查的案件仍在調查，不排除會繼續檢控，「話警方只係檢控 207 人，係言之尚早」，而在 1,400 多人中，有多少是被捕後警方無條件釋放，江永祥指未有數字在手。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥又表示，由 6 月 9 日至今，警方合共發射了約 3,100 發催淚彈，590 發橡膠子彈，290 發海綿彈和 80 發布袋彈，行動至今有 250 名警員受傷，包括有警員被擲腐蝕性液體、被硬物擊中嚴重受傷，被鐳射筆照眼受傷等，但無提供分類。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥指，警方由 6 月行動至今拘捕 1,474 人，包括 1,190 男 284 女，年齡由 12 歲至 84歲，警方至今落案起訴當中 207 人，其中 79 人被控暴動，44 個是參與 7.21 港島的示威，16 人涉及 8.31 示威，6 人和 7.21 元朗站襲擊有關，他強調警方一直嚴正執法，7.21 元朗襲擊亦是警方調查重點案件之一。<br />\n<br />\n他又強調目前有 207 人被檢控，不代表只是檢控 207 人，只是部分被捕人士，經和律政司研究有足夠證據或指控嚴重，會選擇即時檢控，保釋候查代表案件仍調查中，不排除繼續檢控。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AD%E6%9C%88%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E6%8B%98%E8%BF%91-1-500-%E4%BA%BA-%E5%83%85%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7-207-%E4%BA%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%258B%2598%25E8%25BF%2591-1-500-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%2583%2585%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7-207-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG12CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=f85ba179\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%258B%2598%25E8%25BF%2591-1-500-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%2583%2585%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7-207-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&h=e6bfe95f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AD%E6%9C%88%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E6%8B%98%E8%BF%91-1-500-%E4%BA%BA-%E5%83%85%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7-207-%E4%BA%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95/</a>"},{"pid":"e906ceb8787da1a9a94d836dd7a3838f3edb7f4f","tid":1583894,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"b2e51853175643db1d5e3714ecef4c474799d0d6","tid":1583894,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"721    811     831"},{"pid":"9a234bad861fbd89f4b98f25b484096baa0d6f43","tid":1583894,"uid":85552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:45:24.000Z","msg":"即係1293人告唔入或者唔關事<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔算濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe393bfcb15cb7423ba7fa84e9f42b24978ebcf8","tid":1583894,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6f3d0fb908619edebe1b4935b3749f23614c30","tid":1583894,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a234bad861fbd89f4b98f25b484096baa0d6f43","tid":1583894,"uid":85552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:45:24.000Z","msg":"即係1293人告唔入或者唔關事<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔算濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:50:17.000Z","msg":"1293人有無被粗暴迫供？"},{"pid":"1c42f92c4da5391ce3e1d84526dacacbc7c6f42b","tid":1583894,"ui